<article class="post--single post-62 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-uncategorized tag-george-bilgere tag-oklahoma tag-oklahoma-arts-institute tag-poetry tag-quartz-mountain tag-ruth-schwartz tag-teaching tag-teenage-angst tag-writing" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
