    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Been there too.  One night I attended a poet reading by a famous Greek poet.  She leaned her head back and crossed her arms across her chest and recited her poems.  My head just about exploded.  In one, she talked about tits, and cunts and ass while little blue haired old ladies sat in the front row.  I watched them to see their reactions.  They had none.  It was pretty incredible.</p>
    </div>

