    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly! Your blog is the first one I ever read and the only one I always kept reading and still read now all those years later. I love your writing, and what you write about and how it just feels real. You follow your dreams and do great stuff, but you still seem like yourself and a normal human being and that, to me, especially within the current blogosphere, is so very inspiring. So thank you!</p>
    </div>

